[normal]              
[normal]Cuts policy about right
[normal]              
[normal]Given global emissions, the rate of cuts needs to be increased so as to attempt to avoid serious warming.  However both pragmatically, and in actuality (as the UK is only responsible for a small proportion of global emissions), this is not possible.  Curre
[normal]nt 
[normal]UK 
[normal]policies are therefore probably about right.
