[normal]have never received research grants or in the past three decades been employed by a research institute or energy sector employer.  My most recent climate-change-related work of substance was 
[normal]Climate Change: Biological and Human Aspects
[normal] (2013) from Cambridg
[normal]e U. Press.  My views are therefore not 
[normal]prejudiced
[normal] by monetary concerns from industry or academia, other than indirectly in the form of book royalties should any from those sectors purchase my texts.
